    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E92 M3, meticulously preserved in concours-level condition. This specimen features the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering linear power delivery up to an 8,400 RPM redline. The induction note from the eight individual throttle bodies is crisp, complemented by a factory-spec exhaust system. Mechanically, the vehicle is superlative; preventative maintenance including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service has been documented to ensure long-term reliability. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate engagement, paired with a Variable M Differential Lock for optimal lateral dynamics. The chassis remains taut, equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) providing adaptable damping rates. No subframe fatigue or fluid seepage is present. This is a turn-key example for the discerning collector seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
      "price": 46500.0,
