    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that truly defines 'showroom quality.' Every inch of this car has been meticulously cared for by a single, non-smoking owner and kept in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with a professional ceramic coating recently applied\u2014you will not find a single stone chip, door ding, or swirl mark across the body. The factory alloy wheels are pristine, devoid of any curb rash, and wrapped in high-performance tires. Inside, the cabin feels and smells like new. The premium leather upholstery shows zero bolster wear, the carpets are spotless under the original floor mats, and the dashboard remains free of any UV fading or rattles. Every switch, dial, and electronic feature operates exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a complete, documented service history from the original dealership. It drives tight, quiet, and powerful. Included with the sale are both original keys, all owner\u2019s manuals, and a custom-fitted car cover. This is a collector-grade example prepared for the most discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
